Package: scaler
Type: Package
Title: Center and Scale Data Frames
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Andrew", "Tyre", email = "atyre2@unl.edu", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: scaler functions take data.frames as the first argument and
    and return dataframes with the same internal structure. Numeric variables
    are scaled or centered. The constants used to scale and/or center are
    stored as attributes.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: testthat
